[BCFlags "1f"]
[RotationNote "Board 6, chOption: E, chBasis: S, basisKind:Declarer, nOption:1, nBasis: 2, nRot: 3, useStandardVul: true"]
[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "advanced"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/roman_key_card"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST cannot use RKCB at her second bid because trumps have not been agreed. So she bids 
3\H to set trumps, knowing EAST cannot pass after her jump-shift. 

EAST tries to stop at game but WEST is too strong so she now uses RKCB and gets 
to 6\H when EAST shows two Key Cards and the trump Queen.}

